msgid "[vector: polygon]"
msgstr "[vektor: polygon]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1381
msgid "**Overrride CRS**"
msgstr "**Överskrider CRS**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1384
msgid "``CRS``"
msgstr "``CRS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1385
msgid "[crs]"
msgstr "[crs]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1387
msgid "Default: *The layout CRS*"
msgstr "Standard: *Layouten CRS*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1388
msgid ""
"Select the CRS for the layer in which the information will be reported."
msgstr "Välj CRS för det lager i vilket informationen ska rapporteras."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1403
msgid "**Map height**"
msgstr "**Kartans höjd**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1404
msgid "``HEIGHT``"
msgstr "``HEIGHT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1410
msgid ""
"Output polygon vector layer containing extents of all the input layout map "
"item(s)"
msgstr ""
"Utgående polygonvektorskikt som innehåller utbredning av alla inmatade "
"layoutkartobjekt"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1412
msgid "**Map rotation**"
msgstr "**Rotation av karta**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1413
msgid "``ROTATION``"
msgstr "``ROTATION``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1420
msgid "**Map width**"
msgstr "**Kartbredd**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1421
msgid "``WIDTH``"
msgstr "``WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1428
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:printlayoutmapextenttolayer``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``native:printlayoutmapextenttolayer``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1438
msgid "Set layer style"
msgstr "Ange stil för lager"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1440
msgid ""
"Applies a provided style to a layer. The style must be defined in a "
":file:`QML` file."
msgstr ""
"Tillämpar en angiven stil på ett lager. Stilen måste vara definierad i en "
":file:`QML`-fil."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1443
msgid ""
"No new output are created: the style is immediately assigned to the layer."
msgstr "Inga nya utdata skapas: stilen tilldelas omedelbart till lagret."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1457
msgid "**Input Layer**"
msgstr "**Inmatningslager**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1459
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1651
msgid "[layer]"
msgstr "[lager]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1460
msgid "Input layer you want to apply the style to"
msgstr "Inmatningslager som du vill använda stilen på"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1461
msgid "**Style file**"
msgstr "**Style-fil**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1464
msgid "Path to the ``.qml`` file of the style"
msgstr "Sökväg till filen ``.qml`` för stilen"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1481
msgid "The input layer with the new style assigned. No new layer is created."
msgstr "Ingångslagret med den nya stilen tilldelas. Inget nytt lager skapas."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1486
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:setlayerstyle``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``native:setlayerstyle``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1496
msgid "Topological coloring"
msgstr "Topologisk färgläggning"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1497
msgid ""
"Assigns a color index to polygon features in such a way that no adjacent "
"polygons share the same color index, whilst minimizing the number of colors "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Tilldelar ett färgindex till polygonfunktioner på ett sådant sätt att inga "
"intilliggande polygoner delar samma färgindex, samtidigt som antalet färger "
"som krävs minimeras."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1500
msgid "The algorithm allows choice of method to use when assigning colors."
msgstr ""
"Algoritmen gör det möjligt att välja vilken metod som ska användas för att "
"tilldela färger."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1502
msgid ""
"A minimum number of colors can be specified if desired. The color index is "
"saved to a new attribute named **color_id**."
msgstr ""
"Ett minsta antal färger kan anges om så önskas. Färgindexet sparas i ett "
"nytt attribut med namnet **color_id**."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1505
msgid ""
"The following example shows the algorithm with four different colors chosen;"
" as you can see each color class has the same amount of features."
msgstr ""
"I följande exempel visas algoritmen med fyra olika färger valda; som du kan "
"se har varje färgklass samma antal funktioner."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1511
msgid "Topological colors example"
msgstr "Exempel på topologiska färger"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1528
msgid "The input polygon layer"
msgstr "Det ingående polygonlagret"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1529
msgid "**Minimum number of colors**"
msgstr "**Minsta antal färger**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1530
msgid "``MIN_COLORS``"
msgstr "``MIN_COLORS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1533
msgid "Default: 4"
msgstr "Standard: 4"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1534
msgid "The minimum number of colors to assign. Minimum 1, maximum 1000."
msgstr "Det minsta antalet färger som ska tilldelas. Minst 1, högst 1000."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1536
msgid "**Minimum distance between features**"
msgstr "**Minsta avstånd mellan funktioner**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1537
msgid "``MIN_DISTANCE``"
msgstr "``MIN_DISTANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1540
msgid "Default: 0.0"
msgstr "Standard: 0,0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1541
msgid ""
"Prevent nearby (but non-touching) features from being assigned equal colors."
" Minimum 0.0."
msgstr ""
"Förhindra att funktioner i närheten (men som inte rör vid varandra) "
"tilldelas samma färg. Minimum 0,0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1544
msgid "**Balance color assignment**"
msgstr "**Balansera färgtilldelningen**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1545
msgid "``BALANCE``"
msgstr "``BALANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1549
msgid "Options are:"
msgstr ""
"Menyalternativ: :menuselection:`Lager --> Lägg till ett rasterlager` eller "
":menuselection:`Inställningar --> Verktygsrader --> Digitalisering`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1551
msgid "0 --- By feature count"
msgstr "0 --- Enligt antal funktioner"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1553
msgid ""
"Attempts to assign colors so that the count of features assigned to each "
"individual color index is balanced."
msgstr ""
"Försök att tilldela färger så att antalet funktioner som tilldelas varje "
"enskilt färgindex är balanserat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1557
msgid "1 --- By assigned area"
msgstr "1 --- Per tilldelat område"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1559
msgid ""
"Assigns colors so that the total area of features assigned to each color is "
"balanced. This mode can be useful to help avoid large features resulting in "
"one of the colors appearing more dominant on a colored map."
msgstr ""
"Tilldelar färger så att den totala ytan av objekt som tilldelats varje färg "
"är balanserad. Det här läget kan vara användbart för att undvika att stora "
"objekt resulterar i att en av färgerna blir mer dominerande på en färgkarta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1565
msgid "2 --- By distance between colors"
msgstr "2 --- Avståndet mellan färgerna"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1567
msgid ""
"Assigns colors in order to maximize the distance between features of the "
"same color. This mode helps to create a more uniform distribution of colors "
"across a map."
msgstr ""
"Tilldelar färger i syfte att maximera avståndet mellan objekt med samma "
"färg. Detta läge bidrar till att skapa en mer enhetlig fördelning av färger "
"över en karta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1572
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1595
msgid "**Colored**"
msgstr "**Färgad**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1577
msgid "Specify the output layer. :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr "Ange utdatalagret. :ref:`En av <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1598
msgid "Polygon vector layer with an added ``color_id`` column"
msgstr "Polygonvektorlager med en tillagd kolumn ``color_id``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1603
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:topologicalcoloring``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``qgis:topologisk kolorering``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1613
msgid "Transfer annotations from main layer"
msgstr "Överför anteckningar från huvudlagret"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1615
msgid ""
"Transfers all :ref:`annotations <annotation_layer>` from the main annotation"
" layer in a project to a new annotation layer. Items placement can then be "
"adjusted within the layer stack."
msgstr ""
"Överför alla :ref:`annotationer <annotation_layer>` från "
"huvudannoteringslagret i ett projekt till ett nytt annoteringslager. "
"Objektens placering kan sedan justeras inom lagerstapeln."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1630
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1649
msgid "**New layer name**"
msgstr "**Nytt namn på lagret**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1631
msgid "``LAYER_NAME``"
msgstr "``LAYER_NAME``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1634
msgid "Default: 'Annotations'"
msgstr "Standard: \"Anteckningar"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1635
msgid "Name of the annotations layer to create"
msgstr "Namn på det annoteringslager som ska skapas"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1652
msgid "A layer with items from the main annotation layer"
msgstr "Ett lager med objekt från det huvudsakliga annoteringslagret"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1657
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:transferannotationsfrommain``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ```native:överförannotationerfrånhuvudet``"
